            <note xml:id="foot.f1">Dallinger had sent CD a copy of his paper ‘On the life history of a minute septic organism: with an account of experiments made to determine its thermal death-point’ (<ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_10563.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Dallinger 1878</ref>; see <ref target="./DCP-LETT-11576.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter from W. H. Dallinger, 29 June 1878</ref>).</note>
